{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 612629, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "142317", "body": "Anyone have an idea as to the \"Master\" he's trying to summon?", "date": "2009-02-17T05:01:56-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Perhaps Mal'ganis? Lich King it can't be since they are enemies...", "creationdate": "2009-02-19T00:24:27-06:00", "id": 389448, "rating": 0, "commentid": 612629, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "303859", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Kil'jaeden, almost certain LOL. It cant be Mal'ganis, because that 'voice' treats Varimathras like an inferior being and Mal'ganis is equal to Varimathras if not weaker.", "creationdate": "2009-02-19T15:48:11-06:00", "id": 389604, "rating": 0, "commentid": 612629, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "166496", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Most likely Kil'jaeden.  EDIT: Turns out it's Sargeras :O", "creationdate": "2009-02-27T10:37:25-06:00", "id": 82751, "rating": 17, "commentid": 612629, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "garymce", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "it's kil'jaedan because the only other master of the legion is Sargeras and he cant be summoned from such a weak portal, the only portal that could summon sargeras would a LOOOOONG time to make and it would require power equal to that of the world tree, thats the entire reason archimonde attacked the tree, to attempt to summon sargeras", "creationdate": "2009-07-16T20:39:36-05:00", "id": 415970, "rating": 0, "commentid": 612629, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "426892", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 635746, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "309613", "body": "No, Garymce, it is not Kil'jaeden as he is already being summoned at Quel'Danas in the Sunwell, the person Varimathras is talking about is Sargeras the Destroyer of Worlds, creator of the legion.", "date": "2009-03-08T14:33:49-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Come on.. you need a WHOLE Sunwell to summon JUST Kil'jaeden and the biggest lich (and 30 min) to summon Archimonde...Do you [u][b]seriously[/b][/u] think that one simple Dread Lord will be able to summon Sargeras <The blablabla...>?", "creationdate": "2009-04-26T10:18:15-05:00", "id": 94095, "rating": 25, "commentid": 635746, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "mitro", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Its more likely an avatar of sargeras and not sargeras himself. If you look at earlyer Wc history so has sargeras walked on azeroth in other avatars before and he has a part of hes power anyway.", "creationdate": "2009-06-07T10:55:25-05:00", "id": 102440, "rating": 4, "commentid": 635746, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "314577", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "A soundfile was added in with 3.2 that appears to be part of a conversation between Sargeras and Varimathras:  Sargeras:  You have failed me Varimathras!  Perhaps he was trying to summon him to Undercity.  Edit:  If you do the wrath gate questline on a horde character you can hear this soundfile echoing through one of the portals Varimathras is opening.", "creationdate": "2009-07-26T15:11:39-05:00", "id": 111934, "rating": 4, "commentid": 635746, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "7784", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "You raise a point....I mean considering what it\u2019s taken to summon these friken Errdar C.E.O.\u2019s in warraft3 and BC, Id would probably Wright a complaint to Blizzard asking them wtf are they thinking if Sargarous himself showed up. But then again that little noob from ToC, Wilfred Flizzlebang summoned Lord Jaraxxus all by himself in less than 5 seconds, and then got vaporized; so if he can do that maybe I wouldn\u2019t be too surprised if a big bad Dread Lord like Varimathras pulled it off, but he didn\u2019t\u2026..right?", "creationdate": "2010-05-10T23:42:04-05:00", "id": 449601, "rating": 0, "commentid": 635746, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "361391", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
