{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 8218, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "1515", "body": "This big boy has insane amounts of health. Below is a rare video of him being killed, but it took an entire guild over ten minutes to bring him down.\r\n\r\nhttp://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=2156731709954982641", "date": "2006-12-07T03:21:34-06:00", "rating": 31, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "In hopes of reducing the amount of comments about not being able to turn in quests after Wrathgate, a new NPC will be introduced in patch 3.3 who will take Varimathras' place.  Sources: [url=http://forums.worldofwarcraft.com/thread.html?topicId=19820328307&sid=1&pageNo=1] Blue post on official WoW forum[/url] [url=http://www.wowwiki.com/Bragor_Bloodfist]WoWWiki page concerning the replacement NPC[/url]  So there is hope for those of you with those pesky quests in your log that you can't turn in cause the big ugly is gone!  For those of you that are impatient and want to complete your Loremaste", "creationdate": "2006-12-07T03:21:35-06:00", "id": 432904, "rating": 9, "commentid": 8218, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "AmicaGL", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Great video. However, the reason he seem to have a nearly infinite ammount of hp is due to the fact that he Life Drains the entire raid. Don't know how to escape this spell, but it certainly must be interrupted if you dont wanna spend too much time killing him.", "creationdate": "2007-05-14T09:32:33-05:00", "id": 7488, "rating": 25, "commentid": 8218, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "51086", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "lol that was good", "creationdate": "2007-09-20T10:43:52-05:00", "id": 311640, "rating": 0, "commentid": 82