{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 103696, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "14640", "body": "We killed him yesterday after killing Sylvanas.  He does AoE shadowbolts and AoE life drain.  He really doesn't have much hp though, so he dropped like a rock.  Switch his HP with Sylvanas it might be challenging.  He is chained to the warmaster to the right as you enter the room, so hug the left if you don't want to pull him as you enter.\n\nVideo of our kills: http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=-2649424128324653563", "date": "2007-06-13T13:18:28-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
