{"commentv2": 1, "number": 25, "id": 472438, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Domir", "body": "My suggestion is to do ALL quests that start at, or end at him before doing the quest line that makes him disappear. Well, only if you are going for that lore master achievement. Otherwise don't worry about it", "date": "2008-11-26T19:16:46-06:00", "rating": 10, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "So what if we have quests to turn in, but Varimathras is now gone? Are we still able to get the Loremaster Achievement?", "creationdate": "2008-12-02T19:13:14-06:00", "id": 366376, "rating": 1, "commentid": 472438, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "AngryBuddha", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 26, "id": 482812, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "39098", "body": "Will Alliance raids no longer need to worry about Varimathras? Or will only raid members who have not done the Wrath gate quests see him? Has anyone experienced how that works?", "date": "2008-12-01T13:53:20-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "When I saw a group fighting Sylvanas the other day, Varimathras didn't so much as move.  So I guess he's irrelevant to Alliance now.", "creationdate": "2008-12-02T09:53:22-06:00", "id": 61214, "rating": 7, "commentid": 482812, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Nishastra", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I watched my brother and his guild defending Sylvanas earlier tonight and he only went after one guy. Looking him up on the armory, he didn't have the Wrathgate achievement, so I would assume he's \"gone\" for those who've done it, due to the new phasing system.  I feel kinda bad for that guy though, as soon as he stepped into the room he was floored cause nobody could tank for him. :(", "creationdate": "2008-12-17T00:17:06-06:00", "id": 371771, "rating": 0, "commentid": 482812, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "235468", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I had not completed Wrathgate on one of my Alliance characters, and joined an Undercity raid.  Varimathras was actually there, but he was non-interactive. I could not attack him (I could target/select him, but did not have the sword), and he did not react to me even when I stood right next to him.  This was on Saturday before the most recent patch, which may potentially have changed his status.", "creationdate": "2008-12-17T04:32:24-06:00", "id": 371832, "rating": 0, "commentid": 482812, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Wtcher", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 27, "id": 491517, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "rebsten", "body": "Can anyone comment on what happens to the quests he starts/ends after you do the Battle for Undercity?", "date": "2008-12-05T12:02:19-06:00", "rating": 15, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He disappears.  If you want to do any of the quests that start or end with him, you need to do it before doing this quest line.", "creationdate": "2008-12-22T15:25:46-06:00", "id": 66920, "rating": 16, "commentid": 491517, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bruno", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "If you complete the Dragonblight quest line of Battle for Undercity then you will not be able to turn-in any quests that need to be turned in to him, nor will you be able to pick up any quests that he once offered.", "creationdate": "2009-01-01T10:07:39-06:00", "id": 69296, "rating": 5, "commentid": 491517, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "rweagle", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Made a ticket for it, going for The Seeker title so kinda sucks loosing quests As it is now they are lost. They are looking into it and there may come a solution in a future patch  Was afk when gm contacted but he sent me a mail http://img379.imageshack.us/my.php?image=wowedeo1.jpg", "creationdate": "2009-01-14T07:18:46-06:00", "id": 72621, "rating": 7, "commentid": 491517, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kazen", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Actually, it's possible to get Loremaster even withouth quests involving Varimathras. I have the achievment and still got 3 unfinished quests (2 of them with followups) to him in my quest log, including [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=6144]The Call to Command[/url] that starts the whole chain for [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=6148]Demetria[/url]. So I'm unable to do 8 quests total, which didn't prevent me from getting the achievment.  Edit: have the Seeker too of course, you get that before completing Loremaster.", "creationdate": "2009-04-19T09:29:57-05:00", "id": 92357, "rating": 6, "commentid": 491517, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Chand", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Apparently, his quests will be handled by \"someone\" else in patch 3.3: http://forums.worldofwarcraft.com/thread.html?topicId=19820328307&sid=1", "creationdate": "2009-10-04T10:13:52-05:00", "id": 125837, "rating": 2, "commentid": 491517, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "soledad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
