{"commentv2": 1, "number": 32, "id": 533781, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "zapiks44", "body": "Those concerned about getting the Loremaster achievement should have nothing to worry about. I have the Loremaster achievement and even after getting Loremaster of Eastern Kingdom, I had dozens of quests leftover in the Eversong Woods and Ghostlands. Varimathras is involved in only 7 quests, as this page shows, so even if you aren't able to do the quests he gives, there will still be more than enough quests available to get the achievement.", "date": "2008-12-28T03:19:56-06:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
