{"commentv2": 1, "number": 35, "id": 576912, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "309613", "body": "Varimathras - one of the last Nathrezim aka Dreadlords - the other one's Balnazzar (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=10813) also known as Grand Crusader Dathrohan (http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=10812). They've changed the appearence of him alot to the new expansion. You gotta kill him in \"Battle for Undercity\" in a phased Undercity. A tip is to silence him since he casts Drain Life, but he's much easier in the phased Undercity - if you ask me.", "date": "2009-01-23T18:32:54-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 36, "id": 595533, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "317295", "body": "for those still interested, I talked to a gm today, first thing i asked if i should just dump the battle for hills brad quest and he said no, there is a way to summon him, think dark magic. that was all he would say soooo, there's a way to get Varimathras back, just need to figure it out.", "date": "2009-02-04T15:34:05-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 37, "id": 602012, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "320146", "body": "Does anyone know if he will be replaced after the quest where you kill him?", "date": "2009-02-09T16:58:48-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "As mentioned previously, Varimathras is dead. You kill him during the reclaiming of Undercity. He will not be relocated, and the Blizzard rep you spoke to was likely referring to Varimathras' involvement in the Wrathgate questline, which takes place mostly in Northrend.  I spoke with a GM today, and his stance was one of \"Sorry, you're SOL, son!\"... almost in as many words. He/she very kindly explained to me that it was my fault for killing him without completing related quests, and that there would not be any way to turn them in. While I am inclined to believe that the GM was guessing (he was", "creationdate": "2009-02-09T16:58:49-06:00", "id": 407047, "rating": 3, "commentid": 602012, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "joequincy", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He's dead so he won't be replaced unless they seriously screw with the timeline.", "creationdate": "2009-02-12T13:10:03-06:00", "id": 387871, "rating": -1, "commentid": 602012, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Felet", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I meant if there is gonna be a new archlord of undercity", "creationdate": "2009-02-16T16:42:01-06:00", "id": 80520, "rating": 1, "commentid": 602012, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "320146", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Talked to someone from Blizz on the phone today.  He said that they had moved Varimathras to somewhere in Northrend but he wasn't sure.  I'm not certain if he's already been moved or he's going to be moved in a future patch.  Until then we're just kinda screwed I guess.", "creationdate": "2009-03-05T13:15:23-06:00", "id": 392368, "rating": 2, "commentid": 602012, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "waingarth", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
